biography: Leandro von Werra is the head of research at Hugging Face. He promotes open science and works on building large high-quality datasets and training of open LLMs. He lead the BigCode project, is a co-author of the “Natural Language Processing with Transformers” book published at O’Reilly and the creator of the popular Python library TRL, which combines transformers with reinforcement learning and other effective fine-tuning methods.
